awscc_qbusiness_data_source (Data Source)

Data Source schema for AWS::QBusiness::DataSource

Schema

Required

  • id (String) Uniquely identifies the resource.

Read-Only

  • application_id (String)
  • configuration (String)
  • created_at (String)
  • data_source_arn (String)
  • data_source_id (String)
  • description (String)
  • display_name (String)
  • document_enrichment_configuration (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
  • index_id (String)
  • media_extraction_configuration (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
  • role_arn (String)
  • status (String)
  • sync_schedule (String)
  • tags (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)
  • type (String)
  • updated_at (String)
  • vpc_configuration (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
